item.title: Interesting things I saw this week - 28
item.description: This week I was inspired by this artist and decided to try my hand at this year’s #linktober, the goal is to make a zelda related art piece a day through the month of october, I decided to make paintings in my DSi because that’s what I have and I thought it could be fun to do something artistic even when I’m not the artistic type. Here are the ones I’ve made:
